no imagination, really.

00:22:13.930 --> 00:22:17.660
I'm just-- serious, I'm a
social observer, basically.

00:22:17.660 --> 00:22:19.790
And I've seen these things
and I'm changing enough

00:22:19.790 --> 00:22:23.260
to disguise people and not
get sued, or get killed--

00:22:23.260 --> 00:22:24.260
you know what I mean.

00:22:24.260 --> 00:22:26.240
But, yeah, I couldn't
make this stuff up.

00:22:26.240 --> 00:22:27.570
Plastic surgery for a fish?

00:22:27.570 --> 00:22:30.320
I could not make that stuff up.

00:22:30.320 --> 00:22:33.560
So a lot of it-- and the
characters, a lot of them

00:22:33.560 --> 00:22:35.670
are inspired by real people.

00:22:35.670 --> 00:22:37.754
So they're amalgams of
different real people.

00:22:37.754 --> 00:22:39.170
AUDIENCE: Who are
